keyFacts: The document is a calendar entry for a legal deadline in the case Doe v. Epstein.
The deadline was set for May 29, 2009, at 1:00 PM.
The entry indicates ongoing civil litigation against Jeffrey Epstein at that time.
The document metadata shows it was created and later modified in 2015, suggesting it was part of a later review or organization of records.
